Selector:
selector is used to select a html element on the basis of id,class,tag name etc.

Tag Selector:
----------------
Syntax:
$("Tagname");

Example:
$("button");
$("h1");
==============================
ID Selector:
-----------
Syntax:
$("#IDNAME");

Example:
$("#txt");
$("#h");
===============================
Class Selector:

Syntax:
$(".CLASS_NAME");

Example:
$(".txta");
4(".btn");
================================
Group Selector:

Syntax:
$("#Idname,#Idname,.Classname,Tagname,Tagname,....");

Example:
$("#btn,.txt,h1,button");

================================
Compound Selector:

Syntax:
$("Groped element");

Example:
$(".menu ul li a");

=================================
Universal Selector:
$("*");

